Interface EngineCallableStatement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.sql.CallableStatement, EngineStatement, java.sql.PreparedStatement, java.sql.Statement, java.sql.Wrapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmbedCallableStatement, EmbedCallableStatement42

    public interface EngineCallableStatement
extends EngineStatement, java.sql.CallableStatement
    Additional methods the engine exposes on its CallableStatement object implementations, whose signatures are not compatible with older platforms.
